    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - Maersk India - Experienced Professionals",
    "description": "Join the Maersk India family as a Supply Chain Manager in Gwalior. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Maersk India:\nMaersk India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Maersk India!",
